snippet.title: Arcade Game: Change Lanes (1983 Taito)
snippet.description: A driving/racing game where the player leads a amphibian car of red color for paths and lakes, and your mission is to avoid obstacles and vehicles and to earn maximum points by traveling and finish the race before of running out of fuel.
